{
  "texts": [
    "Interdisciplinary teamwork was reported to be fostered through: (1) requesting and incorporating stakeholder feedback to refine an AI-enabled system, and (2) creating channels or mechanisms to enable interactions and teamwork between and among stakeholder groups [15,50,56,60].",
    "Value creationOur review identified that initially deployed AI-enabled systems often aimed to create value by enhancing productivity or improving decision-making capabilities [8].",
    "However, it was reported that these goals would likely evolve as new input and training data were integrated, reflecting real-world changes [47].",
    "Thus, approaches were needed to ensure that AI-enabled systems continuously created value for their stakeholders.",
    "These included:• Continuously measuring the impact of created value by assessing benefits against risks, managing risks effectively, and identifying key success factors in AI deployment and adoption [37,49]."
  ]
}